      • University

        public University(java.lang.String name,
                  java.lang.String state,
                  java.lang.String location,
                  java.lang.String control,
                  java.lang.String enrollment,
                  java.lang.String percentFemale,
                  java.lang.String satVerbal,
                  java.lang.String satMath,
                  java.lang.String cost,
                  java.lang.String percentFinAid,
                  java.lang.String percentEnrolled,
                  java.lang.String applicants,
                  java.lang.String percentAdmitted,
                  java.lang.String academicScale,
                  java.lang.String socialScale,
                  java.lang.String qualityOfLife,
                  java.lang.String[] emphases)
        Creates a new university object with the following attributes
        Parameters:
        name - name of the university
        state - state where the university is located
        location - setting where the university is located
        control - what type of control the university is under
        enrollment - number of students enrolled at the university
        percentFemale - percentage of the study body that is female
        satVerbal - average verbal SAT score of student body
        satMath - average math SAT score of student body
        cost - annual tuition to attend university
        percentFinAid - percentage of study body that received financial aid
        percentEnrolled - percent of applicants that decide to enroll
        applicants - annual number of applicants
        percentAdmitted - percent of applicants that get admitted
        academicScale - integer value between 1 and 5 indicating academic scale of the university
        socialScale - integer value between 1 and 5 indicating social life at the university
        qualityOfLife - integer value between 1 and 5 indicating quality of life at the university
        emphases - up to five areas of study that the university excels in
